      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 54,
      "message": "Agree to wait for ONAP solution for secrets etc.\n\nMy comment was more in relation to where the certs get mounted to. \nThe main reason for mounting to the NFS with PV was to persist them in case of pod failure/restart. Another concern is the possibility of paths/files being overwritten.\n\nIf mounting directly to BC pod is sufficient then ignore my comment.",
